title: Dean Talks ‘Paradise,’ Caelynn and His Infamous Van
description:
Ali and Rachel are joined by Dean Unglert, who talks about his relationship with Caelynn, his time in “Paradise,” and his van life. Plus, Rachel is back and shares details about her wedding and honeymoon.

Be sure to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
